data.description: This spacious 3 bedroom with flex room, 2.5 bath home boasts 2007 sq ft of modern living space on a generous pie shaped lot nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac. The open concept design welcomes you into a great room flooded with natural light. The kitchen features an inviting island, perfect for gatherings, and comes equipped with gas appliances. You'll find a combination of tile and carpet throughout, providing both comfort and style. For those with multiple vehicles or outdoor toys, this property offers an extended height 2 car garage as well as an insulated attached RV garage, complete with water hook-up and waste receptacle. An electric car charging station is conveniently installed and attached to the solar system, catering to the eco-conscious homeowners. The primary bathroom showcases a luxurious range shower, while solar panels on the roof contribute to energy efficiency and cost savings. Enjoy the extended concrete slabs at the driveway and covered patio, ideal for outdoor entertaining. Plus an 8 ft. wide side yard gate that adds extra convenience to this exceptional home.
